==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subapennine
<hw>Sub*ap"en*nine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Under, or at
the foot of, the Apennine mountains; -- applied, in geology, to a series
of Tertiary strata of the older Pliocene period.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subapical</ent>⟦br⟧
